Query Circles Data
The CirclesData class provides an easy-to-use selection of common queries that are suitable for most use cases.
hashtag
Initialization
Most of the previously shown avatar methods internally use the
```
CirclesData
```
class with filters for the current avatar address. If you already have a configured
Sdk
instance, you can use the
```
sdk.data
```
property to access the class:
Copy
