Get total balance (v1, v2)
The total Circles balance of an avatar is the sum of all it's personalized and group token holdings. It can be queried with the
```
getTotalBalance(avatar:string): Promise<string>
```
method. There is a separate method for each Circles version.
Copy
```
const totalBalanceV1 = await data.getTotalBalance("0x...");
const totalBalanceV2 = await data.getTotalBalanceV2("0x...");
```
