Get group memberships
You can query the group memberships of an avatar using the
```
getGroupMemberships(avatar: string, pageSize: number): CirclesQuery<GroupMembershipRow>
```
method to get a list of all groups an avatar is a member of.
The result rows contain the following properties:
group
```
member
```
```
expiryTime
```
Copy
```
const query = data.getGroupMemberships("0x...", 25);
return;
```
If you want to query the details of the returned groups, you can pass the group addresses into the
```
groupAddressIn
```
filter field of the
```
findGroups()
```
method.
