Avatars can invite others to join Circles. The
```
getInvitations(avatar: string, pageSize: number): CirclesQuery<InvitationRow>
```
method returns a list of invitations sent by the specified avatar.
Th e result rows contain the follwing properties:
```
timestamp
```
```
```
```
inviter
```
```
invited
```
Copy
```
const query = data.getInvitations("0x...", 25);
return;
```
