Get invited by
You can query who invited an other avatar by calling
```
getInvitedBy(avatar:string): Promise<string|undefined>
```
. If the avatar wasn't invited, the method returns undefined.
Copy
```
const invitedBy = await data.getInvitedBy("0x...");
```
